\f1\b Text-to-Image (T2I)
\f0\b0  and 
\f1\b Image-to-Image (I2I)
\f0\b0 workflows. By leveraging the Apple M4's Unified Memory, we are deploying a "Brain-and-Brush" architecture that utilizes a Vision-Language Model (VLM) for prompt expansion and scene analysis, feeding into a quantized Diffusion transformer.\
